OL,3,CBack our attempt to oust Keir Starmer,
OL,4,CSNP urges Scottish Labour MPs
OL,6,FScottish Labour MPs have been urged to
OL,7,Fback the SNP's efforts to force a no-
OL,8,Fconfidence vote in the Prime Minister.
OL,10,FSNP chief whip Kirsty Blackman urged
OL,11,FAnas Sarwar, the party's leader, to
OL,12,F"put his money where his mouth is" and
OL,13,Fwhip Labour MPs in Scotland to support
OL,14,Fthe revolt.
OL,16,FThe SNP said on Wednesday it would
OL,17,Fattempt to force a vote on Sir Keir
OL,18,FStarmer's future with an amendment to
OL,19,Fthe King's Speech.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@bO]
