OL,3,CBack our attempt to oust Keir Starmer,
OL,4,CSNP urges Scottish Labour MPs
OL,6,FMs Blackman, SNP MP for Aberdeen
OL,7,FNorth, said Mr Sarwar ` who previously
OL,8,Fcalled for Sir Keir to resign ` should
OL,9,Fforce his MPs at Westminster to back
OL,10,Fher party's plans.
OL,12,FShe said: "Anas Sarwar has repeatedly
OL,13,Ffailed to act on his opportunistic
OL,14,Felection stunt call for Keir Starmer
OL,15,Fto resign in February.
OL,17,F"At every opportunity that Sarwar has
OL,18,Fhad to put his call into action, and
OL,19,Factually remove the Prime Minister, he
OL,20,Fhas chickened out."
OL,26,@tD@KOUyD@AOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
