OL,3,CBack our attempt to oust Keir Starmer,
OL,4,CSNP urges Scottish Labour MPs
OL,6,F"The outgoing Scottish Labour Party
OL,7,Fleader must step up to the plate and
OL,8,Fdo his bit to end the Westminster
OL,9,Fleadership crisis ` or the Labour
OL,10,FGovernment will continue to be
OL,11,Fcompletely distracted from the issues
OL,12,Fthat matter, including helping
OL,13,Ffamilies with the cost-of-living
OL,14,Femergency, which has soared under Keir
OL,15,FStarmer."
OL,17,FMs Black accused Labour of being
OL,18,F"completely consumed by the chaos of
OL,19,FKeir Starmer leadership" at a time
OL,20,Fwhen families were struggling with the
OL,21,Fcost of living.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@IO]zD@AOU{D@XO]
