OL,3,CBack our attempt to oust Keir Starmer,
OL,4,CSNP urges Scottish Labour MPs
OL,6,FShe added: "After taking the Scottish
OL,7,FLabour Party to their worst ever
OL,8,Fresult, this could be one of Anas
OL,9,FSarwar's final acts as leader. He must
OL,10,Fdo the right thing."
OL,12,FScottish Labour has been approached
OL,13,Ffor comment.
